duties_responsibilities.duty: Load and unload materials by hand and with equipment in a fast-paced environment.
Collaborate with site leadership and perform other warehouse duties as assigned.
Lift and carry materials weighing 25-75 lbs, with the ability to handle various types of materials.
Rewarding production-based pay, where output determines earnings.
Participate in paid training, safety incentives, and have opportunities for career growth.
Travel as part of the warehouse team to different locations, providing hands-on support.

education_certification.credential: High school diploma or equivalent, prior warehouse and/or equipment experience preferred.
